This paper discusses the problem of position estimation using ultra-wideband (UWB) signals, which is a topic related to networked systems (NI), information theory (IT), control systems (SY), robotics (RO), and machine learning (LG). However, since the paper focuses on the technical aspects of UWB signal processing and hardware implementation, it is most likely to be classified under cs.NI (Networking and Internet Architecture). The other categories are also possible, but less likely, depending on the specific focus of the paper.
